name: Titan Run
blurb: Race, upgrade and battle giant air ships against various competitors on the Titan Run!

rewards.reward: SUPPORTER: Thanks from the Fuzzy Logic team!
BACKER: Receive regular email updates & have your name added to the in-game list of backer credits!

TEAM PLAYER: Get exclusive access to the development forum, where you can be part of the development process. Vote on surveys, art selections and design choices. Also includes all rewards from BACKER tier.
DRIVER: Be the first to test drive the game, with exclusive early access to the Titan Run beta! Also includes all rewards from TEAM PLAYER tier.

PREMIUM BACKER: Not only will your name appear in a special "premium" backer section within the game credits, but you'll also receive a limited edition Titan Run wallpaper! Also includes all rewards from DRIVER tier.
LAUNCHER: Jump into the action and get the PC version of the game to download for free! You'll also receive all the PREMIUM BACKER rewards.
GROOVER: You'll receive a digital copy of the original Titan Run soundtrack created by DJ Rubix Cube, plus all the rewards from the LAUNCHER tier!

SCANNER: Get a digital version of the beautiful Titan Run art book, full of original work depicting ships, characters and environments from the Titan Run universe! Also includes all the rewards from the GROOVER tier.
FIGHTER: Show everyone you've got style with an exclusive Titan Run T-Shirt! Also includes all the rewards from the SCANNER tier.

ARCHIVIST: Get a physical hardcover copy of the Titan Run art book, full of original work depicting ships, characters and environments from the Titan Run universe! Also includes all the rewards from the FIGHTER tier.
COLLECTOR: You'll receive a limited edition copy of the Titan Run hardcover art book, signed by the whole team. Plus receive the T-shirt and all the other rewards from the FIGHTER tier.

INITIATOR: Be one of a select few that have the honor to name one of the ships in the game, and receive a framed certificate that commemorates your contribution! Also includes all rewards from the ARCHIVIST tier.

PIRATE: We'll work closely with you to create one of the the pirates in your likeness, and give him a name of your choosing! You'll receive a framed certificate with your pirate and name, as well as all the rewards from the ARCHIVIST tier.
ENGINEER: You'll receive an exquisite 3D printed model of a ship, measuring approximately 20cm x 10cm x10cm! Also includes all rewards from the ARCHIVIST tier.

SHIP DESIGNER: Unleash your creative side and help us design the ultimate ship! We will work closely with you to take your vision and create one of the star ships within the game. You'll also get to name it, receive a framed certificate commemorating your achievement, and all the rewards from the COLLECTOR tier.

ADVENTURER: Go on the ultimate adventure and travel with Fuzzy Logic to South Africa! You'll go: 1) SHARK CAGE DIVING with Great White sharks! 2) QUAD BIKE riding in beautiful South Africa. 3) Spend the DAY WITH THE TEAM, learning about how we develop the game. You'll need to cover airfare and hotel yourself, but the shark cage dive, quad bike ride and lunch will be on Fuzzy Logic. And if that wasn't enough, you'll also get the awesome 3D printed ship, the hardcover collector's edition of the Titan Run artbook, and the rest of the rewards from the COLLECTOR tier!

EXPLORER: Go on a wild african adventure and travel with Fuzzy Logic to South Africa! This will include: 1) WALKING WITH WILD LIONS (this is safe!). 2) A day visit to a SAFARI ELEPHANT PARK. 3) Spending the DAY WITH THE TEAM, learning about how we develop the game. You'll need to cover airfare and hotel yourself, but the Lion and Elephant park visits and lunch will be on Fuzzy Logic. On top of that, you'll also get the awesome 3D printed ship, the hardcover collector's edition of the Titan Run artbook, and the rest of the rewards from the COLLECTOR tier!
